  "body": "We should increase the coverage of the newly created clojure integration tests.\r\n\r\nOne of the most common use cases is to make sure that when multiaccount is recovered from seed phrase, balance is fetched up automatically (on Goerli test network)\r\n\r\nThe test steps that should be covered in the tests should be:\r\n1) Recover multiaccount from seed phrase(already covered by steps) & login (we can start from these steps https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/blob/823fce24570900cd2699fe679867fdf723c13561/src/status_im/integration_test.cljs#L182 or even extend recover-multiaccount-test)\r\n2) Simulate opening wallet tab\r\n3) Make sure that balance is updated\r\n\r\nWe want to achieve the closest coverage to what the UI is actually doing.\r\n\r\nTo simulate in the UI:\r\n1)  Restore multiaccount from phrase `siren jungle journey breeze rigid help marine coffee wink amazing half village`\r\n2) Open wallet tab\r\n3) Make sure that there is 0.01 ETHGo, 1 STT\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
